**Analysis & Recommendation:**
- This connector replaces individual connectors for Gmail, Slack, GitHub, Linear, Notion, HubSpot, etc. (250+ tools)
- The `sendTaskFromACC` parser expects format: `appName:actionName key1:val1 key2:val2`
- Example instruction: `gmail:sendEmail to:user@test.com subject:Hello body:World`
- For complex params (JSON, arrays), extend the parser or accept JSON in instruction
- Health check returns app count; listApps returns all available apps
- All functions are async and throw on errors - wrap in try/catch in router
- Env var `COMPOSIO_API_KEY` must be set in .env or deployment config
